gec_072.topic: Dave and Calvin's shared passion for photography
gec_072.summary: On November 17, 2023, Dave and Calvin discussed their shared passion for photography and nature, exchanging photos and reflections on how capturing natural beauty, such as sunsets and waterfalls, evokes deep emotion and provides comfort during difficult times. They also planned to explore peaceful natural spots together in the near future.
